<section><title>Updating the Lenya website</title>
<ul>
  <li>For further information see the Wiki page <link href="http://wiki.cocoondev.org/Wiki.jsp?page=CocoonWebsiteUpdate">CocoonWebsiteUpdate</link></li>
  <li>Checkout the <code>cocoon-site</code> module from <code>cvs.apache.org</code></li>
  <li><link href="http://xml.apache.org/forrest/your-project.html#installing">Install Forrest</link></li>
  <li><code>export FORREST_HOME=.../xml-forrest/build/dist/shbat</code></li>
  <li><code>export PATH=$FORREST_HOME/bin:$PATH</code></li>
  <li><code>cd $LENYA_HOME</code></li>
  <li><code>ant export-forrest -Dpublication=docs-new</code></li>
  <li>Copy the pages from <code>$LENYA_HOME/build/lenya/export/docs-new/build/site</code> to <code>cocoon-site/site/lenya</code></li>
  <li>Create and copy the Javadoc (ant javadocs, ant install, cp)</li>
  <li>Add, remove, commit to <code>cocoon-site</code></li>
  <li>Login to <code>daedalus.apache.org</code></li>
  <li><code>daedalus@apache.org &gt; umask 0002</code></li>
  <li><code>daedalus@apache.org &gt; cd /www/cocoon.apache.org/lenya</code></li>
  <li><code>daedalus@apache.org &gt; cvs update -dP</code></li>
</ul>
</section>
